    <item>
      <title>司法部正式撤销华盛顿特朗普 2020 年妨碍司法公正案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/doj-formally-moves-to-drop-trump-2020-obstruction-case-in-dc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部已决定撤销对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的 2020 年妨碍选举案，要求法官驳回对前总统的特别联邦起诉，因为特朗普的连任确保他在白宫不会受到指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/doj-formally-moves-to-drop-trump-2020-obstruction-case-in-dc</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 18:26:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克最高法院在权衡投票结果时收到死亡威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/top-mozambique-court-gets-death-threats-as-it-weighs-vote-result</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克宪法委员会表示，该委员会的法官在努力验证上个月有争议的选举结果时收到了死亡威胁，该选举引发了抗议活动，造成数十人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/top-mozambique-court-gets-death-threats-as-it-weighs-vote-result</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 18:02:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高校债券税收减免面临风险，因为共和党的目标是惩罚学校</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/colleges-bond-tax-break-at-risk-from-gop-goal-to-punish-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党在十一月美国大选中大获全胜，这将威胁到一项旨在帮助美国大学以低成本升级校园宿舍和教学楼的小众税收减免政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/colleges-bond-tax-break-at-risk-from-gop-goal-to-punish-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 17:50:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利益冲突规则如何影响特朗普、马斯克和其他富有的提名人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/what-conflict-of-interest-rules-mean-for-musk-bessent-trump-others</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普是美国历届总统中最富有的人，自上次担任总统以来，他的庞大商业帝国不断扩张。当时和现在一样，他习惯于任命其他富人担任要职。他提名了几位超级富豪领导政府部门——对冲基金经理斯科特·贝森特担任财政部长，Cantor Fitzgerald LP 首席执行官霍华德·卢特尼克担任商务部部长，北达科他州州长道格·伯古姆担任内政部部长，世界摔跤娱乐公司联合主席]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/what-conflict-of-interest-rules-mean-for-musk-bessent-trump-others</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 17:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工业联合会主席称预算案出台后英国可能失去商界信任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/uk-risks-losing-trust-of-business-after-budget-cbi-chair-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最有影响力的商业游说团体主席表示，如果英国政府不能减轻上个月预算的影响，它将面临失去企业领导人信任的危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/uk-risks-losing-trust-of-business-after-budget-cbi-chair-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 16:52:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥精英阶层与进步派市长就学校和税收问题展开斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/fight-over-schools-and-taxes-pits-chicago-elite-against-mayor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布兰登·约翰逊当选芝加哥市长时，这位进步政治家受到了该市商界领袖的紧张谨慎对待，因为他们已经对他的前任失去了耐心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/fight-over-schools-and-taxes-pits-chicago-elite-against-mayor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 16:49:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北欧国家将中国船只列入受损电缆调查名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/nordic-authorities-link-chinese-ship-to-probes-of-damaged-cables</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典和芬兰当局认定停泊在丹麦东北部的一艘中国船只可能与波罗的海数据电缆损坏事件有关，并表示该事件“引起了”瑞典和芬兰刑事调查的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/nordic-authorities-link-chinese-ship-to-probes-of-damaged-cables</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 15:56:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>税收反弹导致斯塔默冒着新的福利预算之争的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/starmer-s-budget-pains-grow-as-welfare-push-hit-by-jobs-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 正准备迎接一场围绕其备受争议的首份预算案的新一轮斗争，尽管企业警告称，他们将因税收增加而不得不裁员，但他仍努力通过让更多人重返工作岗位来减少福利支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/starmer-s-budget-pains-grow-as-welfare-push-hit-by-jobs-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 10:52:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DHL 货运飞机在维尔纽斯机场附近坠毁，造成一人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/dhl-cargo-plane-crashes-near-vilnius-airport-in-lithuania-m3wlro2l</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据警方称，一架从德国飞往立陶宛的 DHL 货机在维尔纽斯机场附近坠毁，造成一名机组人员死亡，三人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/dhl-cargo-plane-crashes-near-vilnius-airport-in-lithuania-m3wlro2l</guid>
